```plantuml
@startuml spikecodes_stotra
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor User

package "Frontend (React)" <<frontend>> {
  rectangle "React Components" as ReactComponents
  rectangle "Services" as ReactServices
  rectangle "Chakra UI" as ChakraUI
  rectangle "Highcharts" as Highcharts
  rectangle "JWT Tokens" as JWT
}

package "Backend (Node.js/Express)" <<backend>> {
  rectangle "Express Controllers" as Controllers
  rectangle "Mongoose Models" as MongooseModels
  rectangle "Middleware" as Middleware
  rectangle "Stock Data Fetcher" as StockFetcher
  rectangle "Swagger Docs" as Swagger
  rectangle "Node-Cache" as Cache
}

package "Database" {
  database "MongoDB Atlas" as MongoDB
}

package "External APIs" {
  rectangle "Yahoo Finance API" as YahooAPI
  rectangle "Alpha Vantage API" as AlphaAPI
  rectangle "NewsFilter API" as NewsAPI
}

User --> ReactComponents : interacts
ReactComponents --> ReactServices : fetch data
ReactComponents --> ChakraUI : UI design
ReactComponents --> Highcharts : display charts
ReactServices --> JWT : store/access tokens
ReactServices --> Controllers : REST API calls

Controllers --> Middleware : use
Controllers --> MongooseModels : access data
Controllers --> StockFetcher : fetch stock data
Controllers --> Swagger : API documentation
Controllers --> Cache : cache data
Controllers --> MongoDB : access data

StockFetcher --> YahooAPI : fetch data
StockFetcher --> AlphaAPI : fetch data
StockFetcher --> NewsAPI : fetch data
@enduml
```